<Base title="Transformer Temperature Monitoring Applications" description="Plan transformer oil and winding temperature indication, cooling control, remote monitoring and retrofit applications with INNO technical guidance."><section class="page-hero"><div class="container"><p class="eyebrow">Application engineering</p><h1>Transformer Temperature Applications</h1><p>Start with the thermal variable, the operating decision and the installation interface. Then select the OTI, WTI or digital monitoring device.</p></div></section><section class="section"><div class="container grid two">{applications.map(item=><article class="card"><h2><a href={`/applications/${item.slug}/`}>{item.title}</a></h2><p>{item.intro}</p><a class="arrow" href={`/applications/${item.slug}/`}>Review application</a></article>)}</div></section><EmailCTA subject="Transformer temperature application review" /></Base>
